<para id="fs-idm178775392"><title>Solution</title>
Values of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mi>T</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> and ln <emphasis effect="italics">k</emphasis> are:</para>
